message_text: Here are the contact details of your local emergency services:

Bureau of Fire Protection. Helplines: (02) 8426-0219 or (02) 8426-0246

National Emergency Hotline: 911

Philippine Red Cross Helpline: 143 or (02) 8527-8385 to 95
You should be proud of yourself for exploring ways to get help for you and your family.
Type "SOS" at any time if you would like the details of any other emergency service or hotline. Remember everything you say will be completely private!
